{"tid":1353024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔可以比建制派同黑社會割蓆，關唔關事都好一定要拉埋攬炒","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:30:49.000Z","uid":203322,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c09f7a2bc371dcea72417ba30c25d5b906adf9b0","tid":1353024,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"岩岩聽緊881, 揾左梁志祥上黎講<br />\n<br />\n總結話風：<br />\n1. 我地(建制)都有人比人打，我地話係民建聯都照打，有d係村民黎<span style=\"color: red;\">(想洗白)</span> <br />\n2. 我地反對暴力，入元朗報復我地反對<span style=\"color: red;\">(驚) </span><br />\n3. 示威者如果遊行，我地係支持，但你遊完唔好有暴力行為<span style=\"color: red;\">(呢樣我地聽佢講，等佢冇位入) </span><br />\n4. 黑衫人(或林卓停)  呢d唔搞事就冇事啦 <span style=\"color: red;\">(屌你老母)</span> <br />\n5. 危險就番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論係： <br />\n1. 唔可以比建制逃避責任<br />\n2. 唔可以比建制，黑警，黑社會 割蓆<br />\n<br />\n27號 : 以暴易暴<br />\n28號 : 100% 和理非，遊完即刻散band"},{"pid":"9ff2a3c4bde794e4b9942ad4e1b8a3557da6577b","tid":1353024,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da489958d1f98d6e0f539832cec00077f0dfba1b","tid":1353024,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ede25d173a71948609eb48bcbb3f955263bc3f93","tid":1353024,"uid":161313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d78d9f2939069097511e2857d16a02aaa246853","tid":1353024,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"8e5c04e66bcb36deafb0468c205c725371440b52","tid":1353024,"uid":203322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ede25d173a71948609eb48bcbb3f955263bc3f93","tid":1353024,"uid":161313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f